== About me
I am a Ph.D. student in [https://gsai.kaist.ac.kr/ The Kim Jaechul Graduate School of AI] at [https://www.kaist.ac.kr/en/ Korea Advanced Institute of Science and Technology (KAIST)], advised by [https://kijungs.github.io/ Prof. Kijung Shin] at [https://sites.google.com/view/kaistdata Data Mining Lab].

I received my M.S. in [https://devcms.yonsei.ac.kr/stat_en/index.do Statistics and Data Science] and B.A. in [https://devcms.yonsei.ac.kr/stat_en/index.do Applied Statistics] from [https://www.yonsei.ac.kr/sc/index.do Yonsei University], where I was advised by [https://sites.google.com/view/seyoungpark/home Prof. Seyoung Park].

My research interests lie at the intersection of statistics, machine learning, and data mining.
Recently, I have also developed interests in large language models and agentic systems.
